sql:
SELECT p.paper_id, p.title
FROM Paper p
JOIN Author_list al ON p.paper_id = al.paper_id
JOIN Author a ON al.author_id = a.author_id
WHERE a.name = 'Mckeown'
  AND p.paper_id NOT IN (
    SELECT paper_id
    FROM Author_list al2
    JOIN Author a2 ON al2.author_id = a2.author_id
    WHERE a2.name = 'Rambow'
  )
question: Find the titles and paper IDs for papers which have Mckeown but not Rambow in author list.

FROM Paper p
JOIN Author_list al ON p.paper_id = al.paper_id
JOIN Author a ON al.author_id = a.author_id

    WHERE a2.name = 'Rambow'
)

sql:
SELECT p.paper_id, p.title
FROM Paper p
JOIN Author_list al_m ON p.paper_id = al_m.paper_id
JOIN Author a_m ON al_m.author_id = a_m.author_id
LEFT JOIN Author_list al_r ON p.paper_id = al_r.paper_id
LEFT JOIN Author a_r ON al_r.author_id = a_r.author_id AND a_r.name = 'Rambow'
WHERE a_m.name = 'Mckeown' AND a_r.author_id IS NULL;
question: Find the titles and paper IDs for papers which have Mckeown but not Rambow in author list.

sql:
SELECT p.paper_id, p.title
FROM Paper p
JOIN Author_list al ON p.paper_id = al.paper_id
JOIN Author a ON al.author_id = a.author_id
WHERE a.name = 'Mckeown'
AND p.paper_id NOT IN (
    SELECT paper_id
    FROM Author_list al2
    JOIN Author a2 ON al2.author_id = a2.author_id
    WHERE a2.name = 'Rambow'
)
